{"word":"Kadesh","slug":"kadesh","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Kadesh</b> <a href=\"#/H6946\">H6946</a> <br/> Called also Kadeshbarnea.<br/> A city on the southern boundary of Palestine<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=15&verse=3'>Jos 15:3</a><br/> Smitten by Chedorlaomer<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=14&verse=7'>Gen 14:7</a><br/> Abraham dwells by the wells near<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=20&verse=1'>Gen 20:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=14&verse=7'>Gen 14:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=16&verse=14'>Gen 16:14</a><br/> Israel encamps at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=12&verse=16'>Num 12:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=13&verse=26'>Num 13:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=20&verse=1'>Num 20:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=33&verse=36'>Num 33:36</a><br/> Canaanites defeated at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=10&verse=41'>Jos 10:41</a>"}]}